<p>1 </p>
<p><strong>曝光山东小伙李志刚的故事</strong></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">他叫</span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">李志刚</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">，大家都亲切叫他 <strong>志刚哥</strong>。 </span><span style="font-size: 16px;">志刚哥把家乡的平阴玫瑰做成精华。</span></p>
<p><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201126/e453cb815daf43e58b91381a0fd75544.jpeg" /></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>不动刀就能轻松美肤淡斑</span></strong><span>，</span><strong><span>当地很多网站都慕名前来采访</span></strong><span>。</span></span></p>
<p><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201126/2d611c678ddd4115bb424ee842aae596.png" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
